Smooth Tasks is a fork of the STasks plasma applet.
STasks is written by Marcin Baszczewski <marcin.baszczewski@gmail.com>
Smooth Tasks is written by Mathias Panzenböck <grosser.meister.morti@gmx.net>
Smooth Tasks for KDE 4.8 is written by Sébastien Lambert <opensc@beonis.fr> 

Requirements:
KDE4 >= 4.9 (might work on KDE 4.8)
